description:
As a costumer i want to be able to pay the machine
    with 5kr coins and 10kr coins
    If i dont have any coins i want to be able to pay with
    the blip function on my credit card

elements.name: The customer pays with 5kr and 10kr coins for coffee

steps.name: that the machine is plugged in
the water is available
the waste is available
the machine has power
press the start "button" to start the machine
machine started
there is enough ingrediens for the different coffees
the user inserts a 10 kr coin
the user inserts a 5 kr coin
the user inserts a 0 kr coin
check if there is enough money for the coffee
if right amount then activate button for chosen coffee
press one of the dispense buttons
the user recieves the "regular" that was paid for.
